  ('medical-tech-moex-20922', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關人類αβT細胞性質之敘述何者正確？ 只能認識卵磷質（phospholipid）之抗原 為身體大部份的T細胞，其T細胞受體（TCR）由αβ兩條分子鏈構成 絕大部份為CD4-, CD8-的T細胞 T細胞成熟過程中T細胞受體（TCR）經過體基因超變異（somatic hypermutation）的步驟', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:16+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1d862fed5162", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5c7487e6a69d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
